title: Passport - Collection (27albums)
description:
Passport and Klaus Doldinger collection of 27 albums compiled from different torrent files, these files has been corrected using Mp3 Digs (not normalized) some of these files has been converted from FLAC to Mp3 @ 320 Kbps in order to make a standard directory. All songs have been retouched adding or completing proper information as song's name, album, year, cover and other interesting info. Hope you enjoy it like me, and thanks to all people who posted them torren files here on The Pirate Bay and other download sites. Without your valuable help I could not make this compilation.
